Welcome to FOM - Flying Object Madness
developed by: Tobi Baumgartner, Hendrik Simon

--------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------Demo---------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s4X2Fe1Fbjo

--------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------Prerequisites------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

Pleas make sure to install the following packages with your 
favorite package management system.

SDL_mixer-devel
SDL_image-devel
opencv-devel


--------------------------------------------------------------
------------------Install-------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

To install just run:
sudo ./install

--------------------------------------------------------------
------------------Play----------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------

Play the game with:
./run



